window.bookSummaryJSON = "Mattie Ross, a 14-year-old girl from Dardanelle, Arkansas, sets out to avenge her Daddy who was shot to death by a no-good outlaw. Mattie convinces one-eyed \"Rooster\" Cogburn, the meanest U.S. marshal in the land, to ride along with her. In <i>True Grit</i>, we have a true American classic, as young Mattie, as vital as she is innocent, outdickers and outmaneuvers the hard-bitten men of the trail in a legend that will last through the ages."; 
